e.jpg">linkage</a> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukruulltruueshot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kruull Truueshot</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://eq.jokesatwork.com/pics/memorialguy.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/4/01 7:07:27 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> hehe &quot;you make a rude gesture&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uravenwingedangel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravenwinged Angel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/4/01 11:32:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> How do you bring that menu up?<br>
<br>
Or does it come up automatically when you log in the character for the first time? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uslinkkardia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Slink Kardia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 12:39:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> from what I've been told, type    /face    <br>
that will bring up the menu, and I was told you can change it as many times as you want. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urhaski.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhaski</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.wi.rr.com/aggybong/eqpics/evilgrin.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 12:51:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> You can change it as many times as you want, but it won't stick after you zone. Very annoying.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uravenwingedangel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravenwinged Angel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 1:55:56 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> You mean it reverts to your original face, or that it reverts to the first custom face you made when you zone? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uwanderwind.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wanderwind</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 2:04:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> /facepick <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upeeshank.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Peeshank</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 2:36:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> Aye...its /facepick...its pretty neat but is anyone else having a hard time makeing the changes stay?...they seem to stay for a while and then I'll open my inventory and see my hair or beard has totally changed! Wierd.<br>
<br>
Peeshank Pilx <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upherret.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pherret</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 3:23:06 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> yep.  sometimes it sticks, sometimes it doesnt. and if you use an illusion it will change entirely. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utrisden.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Trisden</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 3:30:31 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> The Velious helm I have doesn't have a graphic to other people, instead when I put it on they see my face reverts to the default. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugaiad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GaIad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 5:14:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~</span><hr size=1> outstanding bs if people can change their faces as often as they want too,nice idea wtg VI <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufrice.showPublicProfile?language=EN>frice</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 5:19:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> you can only change it over and over temporarily, i assume in the next patch or two they will fix the bugs with it, so the faces actually save (from zone to zone, helm to helm, illusion to illusion).<br>
<br>
then im guessing a patch or 2 later theyll tell you that they will be permanent next patch, and you can pick your final style before that date... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umojak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mojak</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 8:15:45 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> They need to fix the Dark elf Beard Color problem.. Right now the Beard Color button does the exact same thing that the Beard Button does <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upharos1nymphan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pharos1Nymphan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 11:30:17 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> I think they wanted to let people experiment with the look for now but Im pretty sure it said somewhere in the patch message that being able to change it repeatedly was only temporary.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usharak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 11:35:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> The usage of that command is supposed to be on a counter.  You are supposed to only be able to alter your facial appearance a number of times (for experimental purposes).<br>
<br>
However, they didnt implement it correctly (as the faces are not sticking).  Expect this to be corrected relatively soon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unotwen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>notwen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 12:07:13 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Picking your new appearance</span><hr size=1> That beard color problem also exists for Half Elves.  Though I know I've seen gnomes and barbs with different color beards, and not sure about dorfs - but the difference may have been a luck of the draw default for all I know. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustormwind.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stormwind</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 3:07:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Rogues should get this as an ability</span><hr size=1> Is it just more, or do you think the /facepick option should be available to rouges permanently? It would fit in nicely RP'ing them as a disguise. It also be nice if enchanters had it permanently as a castable illusion.. Of course I think Enchanters should also have a castable change sex illusion too, so maybe I'm just a nut <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=anneli>Anneli</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 4:07:12 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> /facepick</span><hr size=1> Be aware that if you alter your face, and then turn the new character models off- you no longer have the face you had before.<br>
<br>
I tried to get back to where I was, but toggling the new images on and off causes my computer to crash, and not even warm-boot crash.  I have to do a cold reboot to get it going again <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
 <br>
<br>
Anneli<br>
Rake  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvinassolamnus01.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vinas Solamnus01</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/01 7:01:06 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /facepick</span><hr size=1> It seems to me that some things SHOULD be able to change, i mean my human male is fully grown how come i cant grow a beard sometime? I mean sure i cant change my hair color or eye color in Norrath but why shouldnt i be able to grow a beard if its now changeable so i can do it?<br>
I think beards/moustaches should stick, and  thats all imo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showMessage?topicID=8913.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showMessage?topicID=8917.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.emailToFriend?topicID=8868.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.threadControl?topicID=8868.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8868.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8868.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesa